race.comment: BETTA THAN PRESLEY (1) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in six of seven overall and strikes a very winnable contest here. Has placed two from two over this distance range and should be right there when the whips are cracking. EMSIES GIRL (4) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown ability at the trials and won't need to be a superstar to be competitive against this lot. Respect from the Gollan camp. NINJASK (7) has been well in the betting in both career outings and where there's smoke there's fire. Include with the claim. HELLARIOUS (5) is another on debut but trust that she is well-educated out of the Sears stable. Monitor market moves. TIDAL POINT (10) strips fitter third-up from the spell and may earn some minor money.
